examples.en: Stand up straight and don't slouch!
Jimmy slouched back in his chair.
He was no slouch at languages.
She's very good with children and no slouch around the house either.
examples.ru: Она прекрасно управляется с детьми и по дому тоже успевает.

examples.en: She slouched across the living room.
Ever since he lost his job, he's done nothing but slouch about / around (the house).
examples.ru: Потеряв работу, он только и делал, что слонялся по дому.

examples.en: She was a keen swimmer and no slouch on the tennis court.
examples.ru: Она была великолепная пловчиха и прекрасно играла в теннис.

examples.en: The boy was slouching over his school books.
Sit up straight and don't slouch.
Sit up straight. Please don't slouch.
